4.jpg" title="Corazón Traicionado - S01:E104" userState="0"><Image alt="Corazón Traicionado - S01:E104" type="coverArt" url="https://cdn-images.watch4.com/1080/3/1673084.jpg"/><Image alt="Corazón Traicionado - S01:E104" type="coverPoster" url="https://cdn-images.watch4.com/1920/2/1673084.jpg"/><Image alt="Corazón Traicionado - S01:E104" type="snapshot" url="https://cdn-images.watch4.com/1080/3/1673084.jpg"/><Genre filter="genre=6a0c2728768cf9b31f6fe02a" id="6a0c2728768cf9b31f6fe02a" key="/library/sections/home/all?genre=6a0c2728768cf9b31f6fe02a" ratingKey="genre_6a0c2728768cf9b31f6fe02a" slug="bingeworthy" tag="Bingeworthy" type="directory" context="tag.genre"/><Genre filter="genre=6006cc18610ee2002c74f2fe" id="6006cc18610ee2002c74f2fe" key="/library/sections/home/all?genre=6006cc18610ee2002c74f2fe" ratingKey="genre_6006cc18610ee2002c74f2fe" slug="drama" tag="Drama" type="directory" context="tag.genre"/><Media beginsAt="1779602407" duration="3274000" endsAt="1779605681" id="6a09b5cfad807884834e9c75" onAir="0" premiere="0" videoResolution="720" origin="livetv"/><Media beginsAt="1779631570" duration="3140000" endsAt="1779634710" id="6a09b5cfad807884834e9c7f" onAir="0" premiere="0" videoResolution="720" origin="livetv"/><Media beginsAt="1779661228" duration="3274000" endsAt="1779664502" id="6a09b5cfad807884834e9c89" onAir="0" premiere="0" videoResolution="720" origin="livetv"/></Video><Video guid="plex://episode/6a09b5caad807884834e9c69" key="/library/metadata/6a09b5caad807884834e9c69" ratingKey="6a09b5caad807884834e9c69" summary="Alberto va a ver a Claudio en su celda y le reclama su cobardía, exige saber quién asesinó a Marco Aurelio. Claudio insiste en que lo hizo Lorena y Alberto lo presiona para que le diga si hay alguien más involucrado, pero Claudio protege a Gertrudis al tiempo que niega haber sido él quien disparara el arma - María Lourdes le ofrece a Patricia como última negociación antes de ir a un nuevo juicio, 12 ańos de prisión para Malena y 6 ańos para Isabel - Lorena localiza y se encuentra con Paco en un café de la ciudad." type="episode" contentRating="NONADULT" duration="3215000" grandparentArt="https://cdn-images.watch4.com/1080/3/1673084.jpg" grandparentGuid="plex://show/68bad9a39aa661c3574d4960" grandparentKey="/library/metadata/68bad9a39aa661c3574d4960" grandparentRatingKey="68bad9a39aa661c3574d4960" grandparentThumb="https://cdn-images.watch4.com/1920/2/1673084.jpg" grandparentTitle="Corazon Traicionado" grandparentType="show" index="105" parentIndex="1" requiresConsent="1" skipParent="1" thumb="https://cdn-images.watch4.com/1080/3/1673084.jpg" title="Corazón Traicionado - S01:E105" userState="0"><Image alt="Corazón Traicionado - S01:E105" type="coverArt" url="https://cdn-images.watch4.com/1080/3/1673084.jpg"/><Image alt="Corazón Traicionado - S01:E105" type="coverPoster" url="https://cdn-images.watch4.com/1920/2/1673084.jpg"/><Image alt="Corazón Traicionado - S01:E105" type="snapshot" url="https://cdn-images.watch4.com/1080/3/1673084.jpg"/><Genre filter="genre=6a0c2728768cf9b31f6fe02a" id="6a0c2728768cf9b31f6fe02a" key="/library/sections/home/all?genre=6a0c2728768cf9b31f6fe02a" ratingKey="genre_6a0c2728768cf9b31f6fe02a" slug="bingeworthy" tag="Bingeworthy" type="directory" context="tag.genre"/><Genre filter="genre=6006cc18610ee2002c74f2fe" id="6006cc18610ee2002c74f2fe" key="/library/sections/home/all?genre=6006cc18610ee2002c74f2fe" ratingKey="genre_6006cc18610ee2002c74f2fe" slug="drama" tag="Drama" type="directory" context="tag.genre"/><Media beginsAt="1779605681" duration="3215000" endsAt="1779608896" id="6a09b5cfad807884834e9c76" onAir="0" premiere="0" videoResolution="720" origin="livetv"/><Media beginsAt="1779634710" duration="3215000" endsAt="1779637925" id="6a09b5cfad807884834e9c80" onAir="0" premiere="0" videoResolution="720" origin="livetv"/><Media beginsAt="1779664502" duration="3216000" endsAt="1779667718" id="6a09b5cfad807884834e9c8a" onAir="0" premiere="0" videoResolution="720" origin="livetv"